description: Creates a group, or batch, of vehicles. For more information, see Create multiple vehicles (AWS CLI) in the Amazon Web Services IoT FleetWise Developer Guide.

nested_items.name: vehicles
nested_items.description: A list of information about a batch of created vehicles. For more information, see the API data type.

nested_items.name: vehicleName
nested_items.description: The unique ID of the vehicle to create.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the created vehicle.

nested_items.name: thingArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of a created or validated Amazon Web Services IoT thing.

nested_items.name: errors
nested_items.description: A list of information about creation errors, or an empty list if there aren't any errors.

nested_items.name: vehicleName
nested_items.description: The ID of the vehicle with the error.

nested_items.name: message
nested_items.description: A description of the HTTP error.
